Configure the daemon,
	cp ${PREFIX}/share/examples/postoffice/postoffice.cf \
		${PKG_SYSCONFBASE}/postoffice.cf
	vi ${PKG_SYSCONFBASE}/postoffice.cf

On BSD systems, update your mailwrapper,
	mv ${SYSCONFBASE}/mailer.conf ${SYSCONFBASE}/mailer.conf.dist
	cp ${PREFIX}/share/examples/postoffice/mailer.conf \
		${SYSCONFBASE}/mailer.conf

Update your aliases,
	vi $SYSCONFBASE/mail/aliases
	newaliases
	newaliases example.com
Note. the "newaliases" command points to postoffice according to the
mailwrapper configuration.

Recommended daemon flags : -bd -q10

===========================================================================
